727908f-a.title: Queens: Rockaway Boulevard - 132nd Street
727908f-a.text:
Rockaway Boulevard, north side, in 132nd Street (formerly
Atfield Ave., showing the former Ludlum Frederick's house.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

727909f-a.title: Queens: Rockaway Boulevard - 132nd Street
727909f-a.text:
(1)
Rockaway Boulevard, at the S.E. corner of 132nd Street, showing
another Abraham Van Siclen house, owned by him from 1860 to 1891.
Another possible owner was S. Vam Brunt in 1896.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
Arnother view from a slimhtly different anole.

P.L.Sperr
